title: 820-3662 orange light, fan spin, no chime, no display
message:
Hi, got an 820-3662 with no signs of corrosion. Charging light on, fans spins, but no chime and no display. 

PPVCC_S0_CPU is 1.76 v

title: 820-3662 orange light, fan spin, no chime, no display
message:
Any history available?
Do you get USB activity, or external video?
Did you try known good BIOS?

title: 820-3662 orange light, fan spin, no chime, no display
message:
Yes, tried USB and external video to no avail.

Do you have a clean ME Bios? Thanks

title: 820-3662 orange light, fan spin, no chime, no display
820-3662 orange light, fan spin, no chime, no display
message: It was corrupt BIOS. Now machine chimes and displays. Thank you so much.
